 * links.column2_title => 栏目2标题:text:Company
 * links.column2_items => 栏目2链接:textarea:About=>/about\r\nTrainers=>/trainers\r\nCareers=>/careers\r\nContact=>/contact|格式：名称=>链接，一行一个
 * links.column3_title => 栏目3标题:text:Support
